name: Hidden Compartment
Lore: 'Standard astromech internal cargo area measures 20 centimeters by 8 centimeters. Some models have a custom compressed (AI)r launcher for shooting flares.',
Text: 'Deploy on any R-unit droid. At start of a battle, you may ''react'' by deploying one character weapon (at normal use of the Force) from Reserve Deck on a warrior present; reshuffle.',
